I am having issues with our RoboRio. Yesterday we were able to drive and communicate with our robot. Today we went to turn it on and the Rio has the power light but comms and status light are not light up. This has happened once and we had to re-image the rio. I am curious what changed that caused this random failure.

I would look for metal spurs; maybe take it out and give it a shake to see if anything got into it.

A short in one of the PWM or DIO cables

Check the battery and power connections as well

How old is it? They take a lot of abuse, last season we died during playoffs as our old Rio just could not take hits anymore.
